    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/2e6c5b81998ac07a52ea6468f9d67033.avif?t=1759136347\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/cd76316be091e07728fb09892ad37b41.poster.avif?t=1759136347\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/cd76316be091e07728fb09892ad37b41.webm?t=1759136347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/cd76316be091e07728fb09892ad37b41.mp4?t=1759136347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>别让这些糖果跑出穹顶，将它们融合为更大的甜点吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你即将踏上一场甜蜜的冒险！组合甜点，准备好迎接甜蜜超标的传奇征程了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集非凡的力量，让你能在任何棘手的情况下化险为夷。把它们融合起来，你或许能创造出更加强大的东西！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越这些充满惊喜的世界，每一个都拥有独特的调整。你能否成功驾驭，融合出前所未有的超大甜点?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/f53beda042877f60766df61aa6dc3abb.avif?t=1759136347\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/fa0e0ff3488da166ff71bc8d319bd6ca.poster.avif?t=1759136347\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/fa0e0ff3488da166ff71bc8d319bd6ca.webm?t=1759136347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325860/extras/fa0e0ff3488da166ff71bc8d319bd6ca.mp4?t=1759136347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线排行榜：向其他人展示你的高超技艺吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以跟朋友开启合作模式！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两张拥有特殊机制的地图！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人惊叹、完全能扭转局面的道具！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义的名字和角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱甜美的美术设计</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勇夺高分，让你的生活也变得更甜！</p>",
